{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Agra: The Wonder","content":"<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>A teardrop in the face of eternity</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><!--more--></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\">Day 4: 3rd November, 2015</h2>\n<blockquote><p>What could possibly &#8216;force&#8217; me to wake up at 5 in the morning?</p>\n<p>A big, white, marble structure.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">I got ready by 5:40. We left at 6. We reached the point upto which cars are allowed within 5 minutes (yes, the kilometre-distance-from-the-Mahal-fact had turned out to be true).</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2462\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2462\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-12-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-12-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=584\" data-orig-size=\"1024,584\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446544412&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.01&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (12 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-12-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=584?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-12-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=584?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2462 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-12-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=584\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (12 of 15)\" width=\"1024\" height=\"584\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-12-of-15.jpg 1024w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-12-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=86 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-12-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=257 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-12-of-15.jpg?w=768&amp;h=438 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-12-of-15.jpg?w=700&amp;h=399 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Small battery operated cars took us from the car parking to the entrance of the monument</figcaption></figure>\n<p>I had a <em>Safari </em>inside my camera bag which I had to gobble down since eatables are not allowed inside (and I had forgotten to take the chocolate out despite having this knowledge beforehand).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Duda took a wheel-chair, and we entered the premises of the Mahal through the Eastern gate.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2465\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2465\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-2-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-2-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=574\" data-orig-size=\"1024,574\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;22&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446536214&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.2&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (2 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-2-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=574?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-2-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=574?w=700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2465\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-2-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=574\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (2 of 15)\" width=\"1024\" height=\"574\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-2-of-15.jpg 1024w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-2-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-2-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=252 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-2-of-15.jpg?w=768&amp;h=431 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-2-of-15.jpg?w=700&amp;h=392 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">We were almost literally walking through an open expanse owing to the hour of our visit</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2463\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2463\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-1-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-1-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=466\" data-orig-size=\"1024,466\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;16&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446536158&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.1&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (1 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-1-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=466?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-1-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=466?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2463 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-1-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=466\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (1 of 15)\" width=\"1024\" height=\"466\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-1-of-15.jpg 1024w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-1-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=68 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-1-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=205 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-1-of-15.jpg?w=768&amp;h=350 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-1-of-15.jpg?w=700&amp;h=319 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Souther Gate. 20,000 labourers used to live behind this gate.</figcaption></figure>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">All Mughal monuments are architectural wonders. The Taj Mahal is <em>the best </em>example. Even people like me who have no idea about architecture will gape at each component inside its premises.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2466\" style=\"width: 900px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2466\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-3-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-3-of-15.jpg?w=900&#038;h=600\" data-orig-size=\"900,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446536416&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;40&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.003125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (3 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-3-of-15.jpg?w=900&#038;h=600?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-3-of-15.jpg?w=900&#038;h=600?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2466 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-3-of-15.jpg?w=900&#038;h=600\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (3 of 15)\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-3-of-15.jpg 900w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-3-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-3-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=300 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-3-of-15.jpg?w=768&amp;h=512 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-3-of-15.jpg?w=700&amp;h=467 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">See that white arch shaped &#8216;gate&#8217; visible through this gate? That&#8217;s a part of the Mahal.</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">There is a line on the ground that starts from the Southern gate and passes through the one in the above photograph and continues till the small fountains that appear once you pass through this gate. If you stand on this line, you&#8217;ll notice how perfectly symmetrical the entire compound is.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2459\" style=\"width: 412px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2459\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-5-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-5-of-15.jpg?w=412&#038;h=600\" data-orig-size=\"412,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;3.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446537013&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.003125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (5 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-5-of-15.jpg?w=412&#038;h=600?w=309\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-5-of-15.jpg?w=412&#038;h=600?w=412\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2459 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-5-of-15.jpg?w=412&#038;h=600\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (5 of 15)\" width=\"412\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-5-of-15.jpg 412w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-5-of-15.jpg?w=103&amp;h=150 103w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 412px) 100vw, 412px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">And each structure is <em>this </em>massive</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">[The workers and engineers in those days obviously had no advanced digital measuring devices]</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><b>Conversation with our guide:</b></p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>Do you know how many years it took to build the entire Mahal?</strong></p>\n<p>No.</p>\n<p><strong>22 years. How do we know? Observe the domes at the top.</strong></p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"2108\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/04/agra-the-fort/3rd-november-taj-mahal-1-of-24/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/3rd-november-taj-mahal-1-of-24.jpg?w=3216&#038;h=2403\" data-orig-size=\"3216,2403\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446535856&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;30&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.00625&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"3rd November (Taj Mahal) (1 of 24)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/3rd-november-taj-mahal-1-of-24.jpg?w=3216&#038;h=2403?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/3rd-november-taj-mahal-1-of-24.jpg?w=3216&#038;h=2403?w=700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2108\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/3rd-november-taj-mahal-1-of-24.jpg?w=3216&#038;h=2403\" alt=\"3rd November (Taj Mahal) (1 of 24)\" width=\"3216\" height=\"2403\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/3rd-november-taj-mahal-1-of-24.jpg 3216w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/3rd-november-taj-mahal-1-of-24.jpg?w=150&amp;h=112 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/3rd-november-taj-mahal-1-of-24.jpg?w=450&amp;h=336 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/3rd-november-taj-mahal-1-of-24.jpg?w=768&amp;h=574 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/3rd-november-taj-mahal-1-of-24.jpg?w=700&amp;h=523 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3216px) 100vw, 3216px\" /></p>\n<p>Each dome signifies a year. The workers made them to keep track.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The following photograph has been clicked by almost <em>everyone </em>who has visited the Taj Mahal, and will continue to be photographed. It&#8217;s probably one of the most cliched shots. However, even with that knowledge, the urge to photograph it will find you.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em>Why?</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Not everything is seen in photographs. The grandeur of this monumental monument will always be awe-inspiring.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2460\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-4-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-4-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600\" data-orig-size=\"600,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446536798&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;33&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.005&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (4 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-4-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-4-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600?w=600\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2460 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-4-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (4 of 15)\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-4-of-15.jpg 600w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-4-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=150 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-4-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=450 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2470\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-6-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-6-of-15.jpg?w=900&#038;h=600\" data-orig-size=\"900,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;3.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446539714&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0025&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (6 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-6-of-15.jpg?w=900&#038;h=600?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-6-of-15.jpg?w=900&#038;h=600?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2470 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-6-of-15.jpg?w=900&#038;h=600\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (6 of 15)\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-6-of-15.jpg 900w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-6-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-6-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=300 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-6-of-15.jpg?w=768&amp;h=512 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-6-of-15.jpg?w=700&amp;h=467 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" /></p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2471\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2471\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-7-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-7-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576\" data-orig-size=\"1024,576\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;22&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446540363&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.05&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (7 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-7-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-7-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2471 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-7-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (7 of 15)\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-7-of-15.jpg 1024w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-7-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-7-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=253 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-7-of-15.jpg?w=768&amp;h=432 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-7-of-15.jpg?w=700&amp;h=394 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">A wide angle view from one of the four <em>minarets </em>of the Mahal</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Photography is prohibited once you step inside the &#8216;building&#8217;. Since I did not possess my Redmi Note during the trip (I had no idea that it would be returned to me by the Kolkata Police at that time), I used my father&#8217;s phone.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2250\" style=\"width: 2448px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2250\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/tajmahal2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal2.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448\" data-orig-size=\"2448,2448\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Micromax_A190&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446540226&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;3.5&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;258&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.079993&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"tajmahal2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal2.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal2.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448?w=700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2250\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal2.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448\" alt=\"tajmahal2\" width=\"2448\" height=\"2448\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal2.jpg 2448w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal2.jpg?w=150&amp;h=150 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal2.jpg?w=450&amp;h=450 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal2.jpg?w=768&amp;h=768 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal2.jpg?w=700&amp;h=700 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2448px) 100vw, 2448px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">The tomb of Mumtaz Mahal. Shah Jahan&#8217;s tomb is placed adjacent to this (extreme right in this photograph).</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2252\" style=\"width: 2448px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2252\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/tajmahal3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal3.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448\" data-orig-size=\"2448,2448\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Micromax_A190&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446540075&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;3.5&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;518&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.019995&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"tajmahal3\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal3.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal3.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448?w=700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2252\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal3.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448\" alt=\"tajmahal3\" width=\"2448\" height=\"2448\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal3.jpg 2448w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal3.jpg?w=150&amp;h=150 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal3.jpg?w=450&amp;h=450 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal3.jpg?w=768&amp;h=768 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal3.jpg?w=700&amp;h=700 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2448px) 100vw, 2448px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Translucent marble &#8211; I was exceptionally amazed by this!</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2251\" style=\"width: 2448px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2251\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/tajmahal1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal1.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448\" data-orig-size=\"2448,2448\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Micromax_A190&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446540051&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;3.5&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;236&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.2&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"tajmahal1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal1.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal1.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448?w=700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2251\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal1.jpg?w=2448&#038;h=2448\" alt=\"tajmahal1\" width=\"2448\" height=\"2448\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal1.jpg 2448w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=150 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal1.jpg?w=450&amp;h=450 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=768 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/tajmahal1.jpg?w=700&amp;h=700 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2448px) 100vw, 2448px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">There are probably more than 28 different precious and semi-precious stones embedded on the inside and the outside of the tomb!</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">There are specific stones which glow specifically when the moonlight hits them (there are stones which glow under the sun&#8217;s light as well). Our guide used a white LED torch to show us how an entire piece of stone got illuminated by the small source.</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify;\">(Probable) Facts:</h3>\n<ol style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n<li>There are flowers inside the mausoleum which have been cut from single pieces of stones.</li>\n<li>Then there are flowers which contain 64 pieces arranged in complex structures!</li>\n<li>Inscriptions can be found on the walls of the Mahal, which mostly comprise of text from the holy Quran.</li>\n<li>As one enters the main mausoleum, the tone of the inscritptions changes from paradisiacal to those of the Doomsday. Inside the mausoleum, the tone gradually reverses.</li>\n<li>Mumtaz Mahal&#8217;s favorite sari&#8217;s design is embedded into the fence surrounding the tomb.</li>\n<li>There are 16 gardens and 53 fountains &#8211; together they signify the year on which the construction of the Taj Mahal was completed.</li>\n</ol>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2458\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2458\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-9-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-9-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600\" data-orig-size=\"600,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446541896&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;170&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.002&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (9 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-9-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-9-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600?w=600\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2458 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-9-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (9 of 15)\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-9-of-15.jpg 600w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-9-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=150 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-9-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=450 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">I barely remember the trip we made to Agra in 2002, however, I do remember sitting on the cool marble. The Taj Mahal appeared as serene as it had 14 years back.</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2467\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2467\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-10-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-10-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576\" data-orig-size=\"1024,576\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446542074&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;75&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.00125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (10 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-10-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-10-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2467 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-10-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (10 of 15)\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-10-of-15.jpg 1024w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-10-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-10-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=253 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-10-of-15.jpg?w=768&amp;h=432 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-10-of-15.jpg?w=700&amp;h=394 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">A contended Duda.</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">A vacation brings a sea change in human beings. It cures people. Doctors often advise their patients to go on a small trip to the mountains, or the seaside.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Duda was our primary objective in this entire trip. She had just recovered from a severe illness and we were always prepared to rush back to Kolkata in case she fell sick.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">At Taj Mahal, she climbed the stairs and roamed around the entire mausoleum. Illnesses, weaknesses, worries &#8211; everything had faded away. The extremely active, office going lady had returned and she posed for several photographs whenever I asked her to!</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2457\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2457\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-8-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-8-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600\" data-orig-size=\"600,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446541847&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;80&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.00125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (8 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-8-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-8-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600?w=600\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2457 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-8-of-15.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (8 of 15)\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-8-of-15.jpg 600w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-8-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=150 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-8-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=450 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Taj Mahal was <em>this </em>much uncongested</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2469\" style=\"width: 898px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2469\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-11-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-11-of-15.jpg?w=898&#038;h=600\" data-orig-size=\"898,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446542952&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;21&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.01&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (11 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-11-of-15.jpg?w=898&#038;h=600?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-11-of-15.jpg?w=898&#038;h=600?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2469 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-11-of-15.jpg?w=898&#038;h=600\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (11 of 15)\" width=\"898\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-11-of-15.jpg 898w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-11-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-11-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=301 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-11-of-15.jpg?w=768&amp;h=513 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-11-of-15.jpg?w=700&amp;h=468 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 898px) 100vw, 898px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">For those of you who know the younger Gunja, she&#8217;s all grown up now, although that doesn&#8217;t prevent her from running around whenever she sees open spaces. Somehow, I got her to sit there and pose.</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">As I said at the beginning of this post, this wasn&#8217;t the first time we visited the Taj. However, last time I hadn&#8217;t learnt much.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">This time, our guide, our hour of visit, having Duda and Gunja as active &#8216;components&#8217;, the location of our hotel and personally, <a href=\"#camera\">my camera</a>, made this visit marvellous!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">And we realised, to learn more about the Mahal, to take more photographs, we&#8217;d need to visit it at different times, especially on a full moon&#8217;s night (people say it&#8217;s magical).</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The following day we were supposed to drive to Ranthambore, but we decided to visit the <em>Mehtab Bag</em> before leaving Agra, albeit not at the perfect time (the best time to visit the garden of Babur is during sunrise or before sunset).</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2468\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2468\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-13-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-13-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576\" data-orig-size=\"1024,576\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;3.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446633084&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0015625&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (13 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-13-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-13-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2468 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-13-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (13 of 15)\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-13-of-15.jpg 1024w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-13-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-13-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=253 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-13-of-15.jpg?w=768&amp;h=432 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-13-of-15.jpg?w=700&amp;h=394 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">This is the last of the eleven gardens built by the Mughals along the Yamuna</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Babur, the first Mughal emperor came from a beautiful land filled with greenery &#8211; Kabul &#8211; and India was dry. After the exhaustion of the wars he had fought, he built this garden as a place of relief.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2464\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2464\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-15-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-15-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=396\" data-orig-size=\"1024,396\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5.6&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446633789&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0008&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (15 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-15-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=396?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-15-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=396?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2464 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-15-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=396\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (15 of 15)\" width=\"1024\" height=\"396\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-15-of-15.jpg 1024w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-15-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=58 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-15-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=174 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-15-of-15.jpg?w=768&amp;h=297 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-15-of-15.jpg?w=700&amp;h=271 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">The guides and several other sources identify this as the foundation of the <em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Black_Taj_Mahal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Black Taj Mahal</a></em>, which Shah Jahan had started to build as a mausoleum for himself.</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Although a story revolves around this, this is actually a myth. <a href=\"http://www.tajmahal.org.uk/legends/black-taj.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">One of the websites</a> about Taj Mahal says:</p>\n<blockquote><p>Modern excavations carried out in the 1990s found that they were discolored white stones that had turned black.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">However, Mehtab Bagh is also a place from where you can get a panoramic view of the Taj Mahal, the Mosque and the <em>Jawab. </em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2461\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/06/agra-the-wonder/taj-mahal-14-of-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-14-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=374\" data-orig-size=\"1024,374\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446633406&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.00125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Taj Mahal (14 of 15)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-14-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=374?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-14-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=374?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2461 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-14-of-15.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=374\" alt=\"Taj Mahal (14 of 15)\" width=\"1024\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-14-of-15.jpg 1024w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-14-of-15.jpg?w=150&amp;h=55 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-14-of-15.jpg?w=450&amp;h=164 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-14-of-15.jpg?w=768&amp;h=281 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-14-of-15.jpg?w=700&amp;h=256 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We have already planned to visit this garden (and the Mahal) again, at the proper time, to watch the Mahal with a golden backdrop.</p>\n<hr />\n<div id=\"camera\">\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Pipi, thank you for the camera kit! The camera was a constant companion throughout this trip (and an amazing companion).</p>\n</div>\n","date":"2016-02-06T15:30:00.000Z","slug":"agra-the-wonder","excerpt":"<p>Not everything is seen in photographs. The grandeur of this monumental monument will always be awe-inspiring.</p>\n","jetpack_featured_media_url":"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/taj-mahal-14-of-15.jpg"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":null,"subtitle":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"181ac391-9cf2-5d90-bcfc-b9654c38740d"}}